item.title: CVE-2023-3345|2024-08-02T06:55:02.693Z -- unknown -- lms%20by%20masteriyo
item.description: The LMS by Masteriyo WordPress plugin before 1.6.8 does not properly safeguards sensitive user information, like other user's email addresses, making it possible for any students to leak them via some of the plugin's REST API endpoints.
